{"tid":220102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大公報狗仔隊　狙擊《消失的檔案》放映會","createTime":"2017-04-27T17:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T17:30:12.000Z","uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9258fd8510f38af82900ed35c0cefb78013b75c","tid":220102,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E5%A0%B1%E7%8B%97%E4%BB%94%E9%9A%8A-%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A-%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88-%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E6%9C%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%258B%2597%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%259A%258A-%25E7%258B%2599%25E6%2593%258A-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AA%2594%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2598%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9db8d892\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%258B%2597%25E4%25BB%2594%25E9%259A%258A-%25E7%258B%2599%25E6%2593%258A-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%25AA%2594%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E6%2598%25A0%25E6%259C%2583%2F&h=2928eefc\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E5%A0%B1%E7%8B%97%E4%BB%94%E9%9A%8A-%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A-%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1%E7%9A%84%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88-%E6%94%BE%E6%98%A0%E6%9C%83/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/a_AlUF3_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fa_AlUF3_1200x0.jpg&h=b4eb43b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打格者是不願露面的義工（下同）<br />\n<br />\n曾與梁天琦打鬥，盧永賢又出動，撞傷現場義工<br />\n<br />\n＊　＊　＊<br />\n<br />\n四月二十三日，《消失的檔案》於灣仔溫莎公爵社會服務大廈，與社區院線合辦致謝場。<br />\n<br />\n社區院線兩名成員交代經過。兩個臨時入場，沒留下資料的女人，在放映結束後要求訪問羅恩惠。羅導拒絕，希望另行約談。但兩人沒理會，逕自舉機拍攝，追問羅導。現場觀眾不忿被拍，與二人爭論。<br />\n<br />\n及後羅導離開放映場地，走到電梯大堂，兩女人繼續狙擊。成員要求交代身份，二人自稱大公報記者，曾亮出記者證，但僅一晃而過，不欲人知姓甚名誰。<br />\n<br />\n其中一成員說，羅導一直站著與她們理論，但為免繼續糾纏，她保護羅導入升降機，擋在電梯門前，阻止兩人尾隨。<br />\n<br />\n兩女人即行樓梯到地下。身在樓下的另一成員，見證兩人與另一男人，為狙擊羅導奪路而出，在走廊與《檔案》的義工爭執。男人表現兇惡，似欲打人。眾人紛紛舉機警告：「咪亂嚟呀，影住你架！」但他為奪路，推義工到牆上，令其手臂受傷流血。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/b_KupAS_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fb_KupAS_1200x0.jpg&h=018afd36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於紀錄片的觀眾和義工，不少都是記者出身，他們清楚指出，兩女人都是前《壹週刊》員工；而男人就是跟蹤過梁天琦，繼而動武的盧永賢。<br />\n<br />\n前《蘋果日報》的記者這樣形容盧永賢，「認真：小心姓盧，永遠激怒人，然後影你。」<br />\n<br />\n＊　＊　＊<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/c_VcYpK_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fc_VcYpK_1200x0.jpg&h=0168049d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n受傷義工於事發後三日傳來的照片。"},{"pid":"9d9500a4dfa96d97d139cb2250da9b92efc3e0c1","tid":220102,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>受傷義工於事發後三日傳來的照片。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有無報警呢？"},{"pid":"d8810970c22a13e26fae4e810fa1488b6e1e399f","tid":220102,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>眾人紛紛舉機警告：「咪亂嚟呀，影住你架！」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果唔報警, 咁你成班人拍黎有乜用？<br />\n<br />\n放上連登？<br />\n<br />\n然後呢？ 盧永賢就會被雷劈？"},{"pid":"8c96bdf0bb550cc83f9d3b46ffb733e9db742ba9","tid":220102,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>受傷義工於事發後三日傳來的照片。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有無報警呢？</blockquote><br />\n梁天琦當日夠報咗警，你覺得有無用呢？"},{"pid":"36e51ffd77379731b21aa813474ac4846560871b","tid":220102,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>受傷義工於事發後三日傳來的照片。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁有無報警呢？</blockquote><br />\n梁天琦當日夠報咗警，你覺得有無用呢？</blockquote><br />\n大陸雞蟲自稱獨派問人有無報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}